Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Characterization' tab

When I select 'Reticulations' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled

And 'Linear pattern' checkbox is enabled
And 'Reticular pattern' checkbox is enabled

And 'Interlobular septa' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intralobular septa' checkbox is enabled

And 'Smooth' radio button is enabled
And 'Irregular' radio button is enabled
And 'Nodular septal thickening (Beaded septum sign)' radio button is enabled

And 'Architectural distortion' checkbox is enabled
